1
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can Hijikata Toshizou and 
his men survive this attack?</i></font>

2
00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This "deed book" the government 
wants so badly to be rid of...</i></font>

3
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If it's real...</i></font>

4
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It must be Asirpa who has it.</i></font>

5
00:00:34,250 --> 00:00:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can get my hands on it, I'm sure 
everything will turn out the way I want.</i></font>

6
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even in this chaos, could someone 
find me if I fired a single shot?</i></font>

7
00:00:48,830 --> 00:00:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, that Russian soldier could.</i></font>

8
00:02:01,370 --> 00:02:08,310
<font size="40"><b>Golden Kamuy</b></font>

9
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:29,270
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#62000d"><b>{\an3}Episode Sixty-One
<font size="21">Bushido</font></b></font>

10
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going in!</font>

11
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cover us!</font>

12
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The soldiers made it inside!</font>

13
00:02:50,650 --> 00:02:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our fortifications on the other 
side all got wiped out, then.</font>

14
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We expected the enemy to make it inside.</font>

15
00:02:57,320 --> 00:03:03,800
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}<font color="#3d0050">Purple: Enemy
<font color="#f18316">Red: Ally</font></font></b></font>

16
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:04,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we wanted to avoid was having 
them all swarm Goryoukaku at once.</font>

17
00:03:04,850 --> 00:03:12,500
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}<font color="#3d0050">Purple: Enemy
<font color="#f18316">Red: Ally</font></font></b></font>

18
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's better to have them 
come in a few at a time,</font>

19
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and fight where we have 
a numerical advantage.</font>

20
00:03:12,990 --> 00:03:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will win this!</font>

21
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will be the ones to survive!</font>

22
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The soldiers are inside, 
and Sugimoto's started to fight.</font>

23
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:40,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you're worried, but forget 
any ideas about helping him.</font>

24
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's focus on what we can do.</font>

25
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to be ready, 
so we can run if we need to.</font>

26
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, your one focus should 
be protecting the deed book.</font>

27
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll help all the Ainu who 
live in Hokkaido, right?</font>

28
00:03:55,640 --> 00:04:00,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so we won't dash 
Kiro-chan's hopes, too...</font>

29
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everybody says Russia's invading!</font>

30
00:04:06,510 --> 00:04:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Japanese warships 
all got sunk, they say!</font>

31
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to run!</font>

32
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You alive, broke-ass?</font>

33
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nispa who looks up people's asses...</font>

34
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like your head's okay.</font>

35
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow...</font>

36
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your left leg's broken. You can't stand.</font>

37
00:04:34,010 --> 00:04:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're doing better than Mansur, 
though. He lost his right hand.</font>

38
00:04:38,940 --> 00:04:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Nagakura Nispa?</font>

39
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys get out of here, now.</font>

40
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to come back to Goryoukaku.</font>

41
00:04:46,410 --> 00:04:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've more than done your jobs.</font>

42
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you do?</font>

43
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go help Hijikata Toshizou.</font>

44
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, I want to be 
with him until the end.</font>

45
00:05:03,550 --> 00:05:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The soldiers who came in through the 
south entrance have caught up with us!</font>

46
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good!</font>

47
00:05:07,650 --> 00:05:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll wipe out more soldiers at the</font>

48
00:05:09,770 --> 00:05:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">fortifications on the 
north and east sides,</font>

49
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and stick our men inside!</font>

50
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ushiyama, you and the others</font>

51
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">head to the fortifications there 
and stop more from coming in.</font>

52
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toni Anji and I will defeat the 
soldiers who made it inside.</font>

53
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grenade!</font>

54
00:05:59,150 --> 00:06:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata Toshizou...</font>

55
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toni!</font>

56
00:06:13,330 --> 00:06:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My nipple!</font>

57
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you!</font>

58
00:06:23,690 --> 00:06:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So loud...</font>

59
00:06:25,690 --> 00:06:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go! Go!</font>

60
00:06:30,530 --> 00:06:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have time for this!</font>

61
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to find Sugimoto!</font>

62
00:06:37,410 --> 00:06:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toni... I can't believe you saved me.</font>

63
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? If it weren't for you, 
I would've died two or three times.</font>

64
00:06:49,430 --> 00:06:51,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shouldn't be alive anyway.</font>

65
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can give up this life if 
it'll keep you alive longer!</font>

66
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, go!</font>

67
00:06:58,180 --> 00:07:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll protect the bridge!</font>

68
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work! Good work! Tsukishima!</font>

69
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Charge! Charge!</font>

70
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have the east gate!</font>

71
00:07:48,010 --> 00:07:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Charge!</font>

72
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:53,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have 50 soldiers who can still fight,</font>

73
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">including those at the 
south and east gates!</font>

74
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. All of you, secure the north gate.</font>

75
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody escapes.</font>

76
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Deploy soldiers at each gate.</font>

77
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lieutenant Koito, 
Sergeant Tsukishima, follow me.</font>

78
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll search the buildings 
for the deed book!</font>

79
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:39,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My ears hurt so much, damn it!</font>

80
00:08:53,980 --> 00:08:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The noise stopped.</font>

81
00:09:00,820 --> 00:09:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so quiet...</font>

82
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never forgive you!</font>

83
00:09:33,890 --> 00:09:38,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll rip Sugimoto apart, and go 
back to there being two of us!</font>

84
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kouhei, want an orange?</font>

85
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move, Nikaidou!</font>

86
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give back Youhei!</font>

87
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop talking! 
We're killing each other here!</font>

88
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Commander Koito?</font>

89
00:10:10,850 --> 00:10:14,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He stayed on the ship 
instead of evacuating.</font>

90
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The gentle lie told by the 
Tsukisappu anpan seller.</font>

91
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've lied so much,</font>

92
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can only feel like somebody loves you 
after you test them with a lie, right?</font>

93
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lt. Koito!</font>

94
00:10:46,610 --> 00:10:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From the central government's perspective,</font>

95
00:10:48,660 --> 00:10:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">everyone here is a rebel plotting 
to overthrow the government.</font>

96
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we win, we're heroes. 
If we lose, we're doomed.</font>

97
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we come back empty-handed 
from this war,</font>

98
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll be put on trial by 
the military as traitors.</font>

99
00:11:03,370 --> 00:11:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I and my father came here 
of our own volition.</font>

100
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we'll accept whatever happens.</font>

101
00:11:09,970 --> 00:11:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if something happens,</font>

102
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to protect my men from the 
central government, I will...</font>

103
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not going to lose.</font>

104
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:20,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to attain it all.</font>

105
00:11:23,790 --> 00:11:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If all you'd done is ask for my 
help, I would've followed you!</font>

106
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Tsukishima!</font>

107
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsukishima, it seems 
you're my only ally now.</font>

108
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll pay for what you did to my brother!</font>

109
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:04,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give back Kouhei's body!</font>

110
00:12:06,370 --> 00:12:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and your brother can 
wait for me in hell!</font>

111
00:12:12,410 --> 00:12:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's blow up together, Sugimoto!</font>

112
00:12:32,690 --> 00:12:33,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh?</i></font>

113
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, Kouhei.</i></font>

114
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, Youhei.</i></font>

115
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We meet again.</i></font>

116
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought I'd never see you again.</i></font>

117
00:12:55,690 --> 00:13:00,050
<font size="40"><b><font color="#f6f6f4">Golden Kamuy</font></b></font>

118
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead of going through all this trouble,</font>

119
00:13:08,810 --> 00:13:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why don't you just tell me 
alone where the gold is?</font>

120
00:13:14,370 --> 00:13:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you prove you're 
really Hijikata Toshizou?</font>

121
00:13:19,410 --> 00:13:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even Warden Kadokura... his dad was the 
one who met Hijikata of the Shinsengumi.</font>

122
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what about you?</font>

123
00:13:28,330 --> 00:13:30,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really an Ainu?</font>

124
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My eyes are blue because my father was 
a Polish man who was exiled to Karafuto.</font>

125
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Polish have been rebelling 
on and off for a century now.</font>

126
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think your real plan was to use the 
Ainu gold to fight Imperial Russia.</font>

127
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And even if your father was Polish,</font>

128
00:13:57,480 --> 00:14:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that would only make most 
people more suspicious, right.</font>

129
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard that the Ainu think that the 
man inherits blood from the father,</font>

130
00:14:05,740 --> 00:14:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the woman inherits from the mother.</font>

131
00:14:10,870 --> 00:14:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not after revenge for the 
oppression my father suffered.</font>

132
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm doing this for the future.</font>

133
00:14:18,330 --> 00:14:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep your voices down, or I won't be 
able to hear the guards' footsteps.</font>

134
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Hokkaido must become a multicultural, 
independent country,</font>

135
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to stop Russia from taking it over."</font>

136
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is our common understanding, right?</font>

137
00:14:33,770 --> 00:14:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can't escape prison,</font>

138
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you have no choice but to entrust 
it to me, no matter who I am.</font>

139
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not good enough.</font>

140
00:14:42,850 --> 00:14:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some things only Hijikata Toshizou can do.</font>

141
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does that mean?</font>

142
00:14:48,770 --> 00:14:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I simply mean that I can't trust you 
to act in the Ainu's best interests.</font>

143
00:14:56,600 --> 00:15:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it was just for me, 
I could give up easily.</font>

144
00:15:00,980 --> 00:15:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can risk my life to 
fight for something else.</font>

145
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Bushido.</font>

146
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:10,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand that, blue-eyed Ainu?</font>

147
00:15:10,850 --> 00:15:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After our defeat at Hakodate 
I was called a traitor</font>

148
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and jailed at the ends of the earth...</font>

149
00:15:18,530 --> 00:15:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I still think about the 
future of Japan, constantly.</font>

150
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The family I love, the 
home where I was raised...</font>

151
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:30,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Japan, the place where both dwell...</font>

152
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I protect it?</font>

153
00:15:33,230 --> 00:15:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And of course, that includes the Ainu.</font>

154
00:15:37,530 --> 00:15:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a personal debt 
to the Ainu, as well.</font>

155
00:15:40,990 --> 00:15:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which Ainu, specifically?</font>

156
00:15:44,850 --> 00:15:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There was a man named Kimuspu.</font>

157
00:15:48,220 --> 00:15:53,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A man with a strange tattoo at the 
base of his thumb on both hands.</font>

158
00:15:55,900 --> 00:15:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find a girl named Kochoube Asuko.</font>

159
00:16:01,770 --> 00:16:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll know me.</font>

160
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found Hijikata Toshizou!</font>

161
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their soldiers are stronger than us!</font>

162
00:16:41,860 --> 00:16:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're in bad shape!</font>

163
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find Lieutenant Tsurumi.</font>

164
00:16:46,170 --> 00:16:48,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we defeat him, that will 
destroy their morale.</font>

165
00:16:48,180 --> 00:16:50,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can we find him in the middle of this?</font>

166
00:16:57,190 --> 00:17:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The south and east gates have fallen.</font>

167
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the soldiers inside are 
attacking the north gate.</font>

168
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when it falls, all their 
soldiers will come after us!</font>

169
00:17:08,700 --> 00:17:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's run! So we can 
protect the deed book!</font>

170
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on at Goryoukaku?!</font>

171
00:17:37,950 --> 00:17:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's dangerous!</font>

172
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're not behind the 
tree you might get shot!</font>

173
00:17:49,410 --> 00:17:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The stable on the north side 
started to burn brightly,</i></font>

174
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and for a moment, drew everyone's 
attention even in the middle of battle.</i></font>

175
00:17:58,530 --> 00:18:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the signal Shiraishi talked about!</font>

176
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's decided to leave!</font>

177
00:18:04,820 --> 00:18:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should fall back!</font>

178
00:18:06,350 --> 00:18:08,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can regroup and come back</font>

179
00:18:08,580 --> 00:18:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">before they dig up all of 
Goryoukaku to find the gold!</font>

180
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This battle wasn't a waste!</font>

181
00:18:14,710 --> 00:18:17,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We cut down Tsurumi's 
army by a lot of men.</font>

182
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:19,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can regroup, we can win!</font>

183
00:18:22,300 --> 00:18:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Head to the east!</font>

184
00:18:23,990 --> 00:18:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They may try to run!</font>

185
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With the deed book in hand, 
they can't try to go through the moat!</font>

186
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do we check the stable?</font>

187
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

188
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a messenger! I'm coming through!</font>

189
00:18:39,260 --> 00:18:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop him!</font>

190
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Shiraishi!</font>

191
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't hit the bag!</font>

192
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's got the deed book and the girl!</font>

193
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

194
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did they show up at the 
other side of the bridge now?</font>

195
00:19:05,180 --> 00:19:06,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagakura Shinpachi!</font>

196
00:19:08,870 --> 00:19:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, shit!</font>

197
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Of course, that bag doesn't contain 
either Asirpa-chan or the deed book!</i></font>

198
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's just some ropes!</i></font>

199
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Asirpa's waiting by the 
side of the moat, though!</i></font>

200
00:19:21,130 --> 00:19:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The quiver that contains the deed book</i></font>

201
00:19:23,150 --> 00:19:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>was waterproofed with diatomaceous 
earth and animal stomach lining!</i></font>

202
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll cross the bridge with the horse.</i></font>

203
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And toss the rope from the opposite side.</i></font>

204
00:19:30,390 --> 00:19:34,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll pull it with the horse and 
get Asirpa-chan across fast!</i></font>

205
00:19:34,190 --> 00:19:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the plan!</i></font>

206
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it failed!</i></font>

207
00:19:38,810 --> 00:19:41,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So swim across and run away 
on your own, Asirpa-chan!</i></font>

208
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:44,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No sign of Shiraishi.</font>

209
00:19:45,860 --> 00:19:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

210
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toni Anji...</font>

211
00:20:08,940 --> 00:20:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He found me!</font>

212
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come at me, country samurai from Satsuma!</font>

213
00:20:17,540 --> 00:20:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, there...</font>

214
00:20:20,280 --> 00:20:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you gotten too old 
to fight, Shinsengumi?</font>

215
00:20:36,290 --> 00:20:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More of them!</font>

216
00:20:48,730 --> 00:20:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your blade is weak!</font>

217
00:20:50,970 --> 00:20:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're no match for the fighting 
spirit of the Satsuma soldiers</font>

218
00:20:54,370 --> 00:20:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I faced 40 years ago!</font>

219
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The deed book!</font>

220
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asirpa-san!</font>

221
00:21:31,810 --> 00:21:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sugimoto!</font>

222
00:21:33,790 --> 00:21:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry! Hurry!</font>

223
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:35,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're coming!</font>

224
00:21:35,890 --> 00:21:37,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The south exit's no good!</font>

225
00:21:37,610 --> 00:21:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are soldiers there!</font>

226
00:21:40,230 --> 00:21:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The east, then!</font>

227
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:42,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That won't work either!</font>

228
00:21:42,990 --> 00:21:44,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The north exit's our only hope!</font>

229
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know?</font>

230
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:49,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think Sofia's still 
blocking the north exit,</font>

231
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so the enemy's coming around 
to the east and south.</font>

232
00:21:51,620 --> 00:21:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means there shouldn't 
be many of them on the</font>

233
00:21:54,430 --> 00:21:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">other side of the north bridge!</font>

234
00:21:56,090 --> 00:21:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's important is what 
happens when we get out.</font>

235
00:21:58,210 --> 00:21:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get away from here!</font>

236
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#62000d"><b>{\an3}<font size="17">Next time
<font size="27">Daughter of Wilk</font></font></b></font>

237
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time: Daughter of Wilk.</i></font>

